{"id": "art-87", "label": "Art. 87", "title": "Art. 87", "slug": "art-87", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 87 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Cesiunea\naportului de capital social este posibil&#259; dac&#259; a fost permis&#259;\nprin actul constitutiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Cesiunea nu libereaz&#259; pe\nasociatul cedent de ceea ce mai datoreaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndin aportul s&#259;u de capital.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;i</span>, cedentul r&#259;mâne\nr&#259;spunz&#259;tor potrivit art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>225</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Când actul constitutiv prevede\ncazurile de retragere a unui asociat, se vor aplica <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>225</span><span style='color:black'> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>229</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL <span class=SpellE>III:Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nîn comandit&#259; simpl&#259;</span></b></p>"}